WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.947
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.947 --> 00:00:03.097
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.097 --> 00:00:04.880
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:06.871
Well, I just wanted to say thank you.

00:00:06.871 --> 00:00:11.620
A dear sister sent this to me for my birthday, and it was really cool.

00:00:12.773 --> 00:00:17.920
When I get something I really like like this, I told Braden, I said, "I'm going to tell them thank you for it.

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:19.200
" I like blankets.

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:20.533
This is really special.

00:00:20.533 --> 00:00:24.888
You know, my birthday is really close to the fourth, and so she said, "I made...

00:00:24.888 --> 00:00:31.146
" I don't know if she made it—I believe she made it—but she got this for me for my birthday present.

00:00:31.146 --> 00:00:34.460
And I just thought I would share it with you and just tell her thank you.

00:00:34.460 --> 00:00:37.040
Isn't that neat?

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:39.189
That was pretty cool and pretty special.

00:00:39.189 --> 00:00:42.810
I said, "Hey, that was really nice of her.

00:00:42.810 --> 00:00:48.720
" But then somebody sent Braden a drone, and he wanted to say personally, "Thank you for that.

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:50.887
" Yes, I just want to say thank you for this drone.

00:00:51.215 --> 00:00:52.528
It's DJI, too.

00:00:52.528 --> 00:00:54.880
I just love stuff like this.

00:00:54.880 --> 00:00:55.400
So, yeah.

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.360
He was so excited.

00:00:56.360 --> 00:01:00.640
Somebody sent this to him in the mail, and he's been playing with it.

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:04.693
Oh, yeah, it has a gimbal, and the gimbals make the footage steady.

00:01:04.693 --> 00:01:06.520
So, yeah, that's what that is.

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:09.626
It's a very nice drone.

00:01:09.626 --> 00:01:14.520
So, we just got these two things today, and I just wanted to say thank you.

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:18.960
Braden was excited about the drone, and he said, "Hey, Dad, I want to tell them thank you.

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:20.160
" It was a young couple.

00:01:20.160 --> 00:01:21.900
They said they played with it with their dog.

00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:22.650
With their dog, yes.

00:01:22.650 --> 00:01:26.479
And it came with ND filters over it.

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:30.539
They took good care of it.

00:01:30.539 --> 00:01:31.139
It's nice.

00:01:31.439 --> 00:01:32.506
So, it's a blessing.

00:01:32.506 --> 00:01:38.684
And he just wanted to come on and just say thank you to the young lady that sent it to him.

00:01:38.684 --> 00:01:40.400
And I said, "Look at that, B.

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.599
You got you a drone.

00:01:41.599 --> 00:01:42.532
" And it goes way high.

00:01:42.532 --> 00:01:45.416
He said, "I can't send it any higher.

00:01:45.416 --> 00:01:50.293
It says, 'Unless I register it, I can't go any higher,'" because we wanted to see how high we could see.

00:01:50.293 --> 00:01:55.691
So, we were flying around, and Diana was in the garage, and he took it over the house and was turning around looking.

00:01:55.691 --> 00:01:58.240
He was making it look like he was waving at her.

00:01:58.240 --> 00:01:59.839
So, thank you so much.

00:01:59.839 --> 00:02:05.147
Yeah, I could use it for the tribulation, too, because we used to go to the temple, you know, like go around it, you know.

00:02:05.147 --> 00:02:13.792
So, I was like, "Hey, yeah, I could like fly this around and put the screens on it, you know, myself," because I used to have to use other people's footage, so I never had a drone.

00:02:13.792 --> 00:02:15.280
So, I love it.

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:15.829
Thank you.

00:02:15.829 --> 00:02:23.189
Yeah, he works really hard, and it was really a nice gift, and I just wanted to honor the person who did it and just say thank you.

00:02:23.189 --> 00:02:24.434
Braden was excited.

00:02:24.434 --> 00:02:25.463
All right.

00:02:25.463 --> 00:02:28.297
Well, hey, you never see him.

00:02:28.297 --> 00:02:37.096
He's always behind the camera hiding out over here praying with me, but he said, "I've got to tell them thank you because it's very expensive, you know.

00:02:37.096 --> 00:02:42.040
" And he's like, "You know, I just want to be able to honor people when they honor me, Daddy.

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:44.560
" And I said, "Okay, let's do it.

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:44.792
Let's do it.

00:02:45.256 --> 00:02:49.760
" So, and she gave a blanket to Megan, too, with a smiley face on it.

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:51.600
And I thought that was really a blessing.

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:53.074
Smiley face blanket for Megan.

00:02:53.074 --> 00:02:54.800
So, yeah, we got some treasures today.

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:56.560
I just said, "Wasn't that neat?

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.759
" All in the same day.

00:02:57.759 --> 00:03:07.246
Got a really cool blanket for my birthday, and I got a drone for my son, and a smiley face blanket for Megan.

00:03:07.246 --> 00:03:09.920
And you know, people are kind.

00:03:09.920 --> 00:03:10.800
People are really kind.

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:12.343
I said, "Look at this stuff.

00:03:12.343 --> 00:03:16.000
We get these little toys and stuff, you know.

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:21.348
" So, just being kind to us, I appreciate that a lot.

00:03:21.348 --> 00:03:37.269
Well, Donne Clement, Kim Clement's daughter, reached out to us and said, "Hey, my dad had a word that was similar to the word that you gave about the weapon that has never been seen before.

00:03:37.269 --> 00:03:45.851
" And she said, "I want to send it to you through X or whatever," and it was a text message, and she said, "I want to show you what my dad prophesied.

00:03:45.851 --> 00:03:47.508
" Well, I had no idea.

00:03:47.508 --> 00:03:48.560
This was amazing, folks.

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:59.680
When you have two different voices that don't even know each other hearing the Spirit of the Lord warning you about a new weapon, a new weapon that we've never seen before, bigger, bigger...

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:06.659
Like, you know, I want to say this, nuclear weapons are a thing of the past.

00:04:06.659 --> 00:04:17.967
And that may sound really—well, boy, Brandon, I don't know about that—but I'm telling you all, technological advancements have surpassed nuclear energy, nuclear.

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:24.560
I'm telling you, we're on the verge of a new industrial revolution.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:36.987
And these new weapons, new things that we've never seen before that will become public, they've been working on behind closed doors for probably decades.

00:04:36.987 --> 00:04:38.400
Who knows?

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:39.950
They gradually come out now.

00:04:39.950 --> 00:04:45.430
AI and the things I've told you about AI...

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:48.514
Did you see Mission Impossible, Tom Cruise, and all that?

00:04:48.514 --> 00:04:49.440
My goodness, folks.

00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:56.240
AI and all the stuff I told you is coming, they're talking about in Hollywood—they try to desensitize you.

00:04:56.240 --> 00:05:03.080
"Hey, you know, AI is going to take over and become the superpower and all this stuff, and we got a Mission Impossible to stop it.

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:05.074
" I just think it's very interesting.

00:05:05.074 --> 00:05:14.880
So, going back to what Kim Clement said about this weapon, he said he saw it in the woods.

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:30.160
Now, I don't know if Poland has woods, but the Lord showed me it went out of Russia and came across and struck right there on the border right there by Warsaw and that area.

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:30.500
Okay?

00:05:30.500 --> 00:05:37.013
And when it did, it made a humongous blast zone, and it went straight up, and it looked like a mushroom cloud.

00:05:37.013 --> 00:05:40.600
And that's when I stopped and I said, "Lord, are they going to nuke them?

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:44.045
" I said, "Are they going to nuke these people?

00:05:44.045 --> 00:05:48.930
" And the Lord said, "No, this is a weapon, Braden, that you've never seen before.

00:05:48.930 --> 00:05:50.799
No one has ever seen this.

00:05:51.119 --> 00:05:53.866
It's never been used on the planet before.

00:05:53.866 --> 00:05:58.080
This is new technological advancements.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:07.257
" So when you hear what Kim says—and I'm about to play the little bit of the word so you can hear what he says, because it's really awesome whenever you have another...

00:06:07.257 --> 00:06:11.372
I had a confirmation that we're on the right road praying together.

00:06:11.372 --> 00:06:13.319
We're on the right road, folks.

00:06:13.319 --> 00:06:19.182
And, you know, when you have confirmation, and Donne sent it, and I was like, "You know, Lord, thank you.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:23.820
It's always a pat on the back to say, 'Hey, guys, we're doing it.

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:25.040
Prayer changes things.

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:29.908
Let's pray into this and pray more and stop these things.

00:06:29.908 --> 00:06:32.936
'" I believe there are certain things, you know, mass casualties...

00:06:32.936 --> 00:06:36.834
The Lord showed me it was like a 50-mile blast zone.

00:06:36.834 --> 00:06:37.257
Huge blast zone.

00:06:38.030 --> 00:06:40.679
This was not like a normal little area.

00:06:40.679 --> 00:06:41.279
This was big.

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:43.330
And I know 50 miles seems like a lot, folks.

00:06:43.330 --> 00:06:46.445
That's a big area, but I'm just saying it was a massive blast zone.

00:06:46.445 --> 00:06:51.382
Maybe it was 10 miles, but I'm just saying it looked huge for what I saw.

00:06:51.382 --> 00:06:57.897
And everything around it, the people were gone, and the buildings still existed.

00:06:57.897 --> 00:07:04.373
And I thought, "That is crazy," you know, the things I see when I'm praying.

00:07:04.888 --> 00:07:14.080
So, and the Lord warned me, and he said, "Brandon, they don't want to use nuclear weapons because you can't inhabit the area after you do this.

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:19.600
You have to have gas masks, bodysuits, and everything else because of radiation fallout, you know.

00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:31.337
" So, like I said, nuclear energy, nuclear fusion, nuclear things are going to become a thing of the past with this new AI industrial revolution.

00:07:31.337 --> 00:07:40.640
We will see energy that we never knew existed in the days ahead through mathematical equations similar to Einstein.

00:07:40.640 --> 00:07:43.320
But we have a computer being the Einstein.

00:07:43.320 --> 00:07:44.400
Do you understand?

00:07:44.400 --> 00:07:51.386
And it's going to be with this Hadron collider and the God particle and all these things that are going on with CERN.

00:07:51.386 --> 00:07:58.800
I'm telling you all, technological advancements beyond your wildest expectations are coming in the days ahead.

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:02.319
And it's not going to be, "Well, we saw a little something in 2020.

00:08:02.319 --> 00:08:03.490
" I'm talking about it's going to be like dominoes.

00:08:03.490 --> 00:08:05.280
We're going to hear it all the time.

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:07.546
"Here's some stuff to heal diabetes.

00:08:07.546 --> 00:08:09.680
Here's some stuff to heal cancer.

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:11.280
Here's, you know, whatever.

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:13.599
" It's going to be everywhere all the time.

00:08:13.599 --> 00:08:14.697
Alzheimer's is no more.

00:08:14.697 --> 00:08:15.720
Dementia is no more.

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:18.107
And that's what's going to get you to trust it.

00:08:18.107 --> 00:08:22.029
Living in this time is pretty wild, isn't it?

00:08:22.029 --> 00:08:24.600
Don't you all think it's pretty wild?

00:08:24.600 --> 00:08:28.000
You know, we see all the things we're seeing.

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:34.000
Some folks never thought we'd still be here, that the rapture of the church would have taken place way before this.

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:36.868
But we're seeing more than what a lot of people thought we would see.

00:08:36.868 --> 00:08:39.960
In other words, we haven't had our revival yet.

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:42.146
We haven't had the great harvest of souls.

00:08:42.146 --> 00:08:44.453
And some people say, "Well, that's not biblical, Brandon.

00:08:44.453 --> 00:08:49.413
It's not in the word to have a major harvest of souls before the rapture of the church.

00:08:49.413 --> 00:08:53.714
It's during and after the rapture of the church that everybody's freaking out and everybody runs to Jesus.

00:08:53.714 --> 00:08:57.102
" I'm not denying, folks, that people are going to freak out and want to come find Jesus.

00:08:57.102 --> 00:09:18.022
But if you remember what I told you, when I went to the Tribulation with the Father and He took me out of my body in an out-of-body experience, I saw many groups of Christians that knew what had happened that had been left behind, that did not keep their lamps full of oil, that were lukewarm.

00:09:18.022 --> 00:09:21.200
They were not filled with or controlled by the Holy Ghost at all.

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:23.859
They were living a compromising life, and they got left.

00:09:23.859 --> 00:09:26.178
And I'm telling you, they were mad.

00:09:26.178 --> 00:09:28.222
Oh, they were so mad.

00:09:28.222 --> 00:09:31.749
And when this happened, they were ready to string up those preachers.

00:09:31.749 --> 00:09:34.000
I'm talking hang them right there.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:34.660
It was bad.

00:09:34.660 --> 00:09:38.526
They were ready to hang those preachers for not preaching more fiery words.

00:09:38.526 --> 00:09:39.360
They blamed them.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:44.631
Instead of blaming themselves for being lukewarm, they blamed their preachers, the preachers who were left here.

00:09:44.631 --> 00:09:51.029
And I told you, I saw certain preachers that were here that have been on television.

00:09:51.029 --> 00:09:59.570
And I'm telling you all, these men were preaching to millions and millions of people on a weekly basis.

00:09:59.570 --> 00:10:11.234
So if I told you their names of who I saw, which I'm never going to do—if I told you their names who were here, you would go, "Oh my gosh.

00:10:11.234 --> 00:10:22.760
" Seriously, I still see them and I watch, and I always tell—because my son knows and my wife—and we go, "Turn the channel quick.

00:10:22.760 --> 00:10:31.419
" I'm not going to let them feed me because I know who's here, parts of the people out of that little vision of what the Lord showed me, whatever this was.

00:10:31.419 --> 00:10:36.697
I want to play the clip for you and I think it'll bless you.

00:10:36.697 --> 00:10:39.440
So we'll be right back after this.

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:43.920
I suddenly became aware of danger and it seemed like there were signs of war.

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:50.459
What frightened me was that there was talk of a destructive weapon and I heard this: "They're looking in the wrong place.

00:10:50.459 --> 00:10:51.699
It's hidden.

00:10:51.699 --> 00:11:01.519
" And so, it's like I was catapulted hundreds of feet into the air and I was above a large forest.

00:11:01.519 --> 00:11:03.456
Now, I think some of you even heard me say that.

00:11:03.456 --> 00:11:08.959
And I was hovering above this massive forest.

00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:18.750
The color seemed dusty with hints of yellow and mustard—it's like mustard or yellow.

00:11:18.750 --> 00:11:21.168
It didn't seem like a normal forest.

00:11:21.168 --> 00:11:24.672
And this country contains something extremely dangerous.

00:11:24.672 --> 00:11:34.600
I was aware of the fact that as a prophet in this age, I was in a similar position as Elisha was when he started seeing and hearing the plans of the enemy.

00:11:34.600 --> 00:11:38.560
I became aware of extreme heat and danger.

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:48.520
My body was overwhelmed by what was like radiance and fire, and fear struck me for the first time.

00:11:48.520 --> 00:11:50.380
And that's when I said, "It's okay.

00:11:50.380 --> 00:11:55.880
It's okay," because I was trying to tell somebody that was in this vision.

00:11:55.880 --> 00:11:59.794
But fear struck me for the first time.

00:11:59.794 --> 00:12:01.165
Was this nuclear?

00:12:01.165 --> 00:12:02.439
Was this atomic?

00:12:02.439 --> 00:12:07.120
Was this what I was feeling?

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:10.060
Was I interceding on behalf of Israel and America?

00:12:10.060 --> 00:12:12.183
I believe I was, first of all.

00:12:12.183 --> 00:12:27.733
But at that point there were multiple visions and a question seemed to arise constantly: Armageddon, the slaughter of humanity, an atomic war no one wanted but which no one had the wisdom to avoid.

00:12:27.733 --> 00:12:44.079
Now I need to say that to you again and I want you to listen to it because this is what I heard: Armageddon, the slaughter of humanity, an atomic war no one wanted but which no one had the wisdom to avoid.

00:12:44.079 --> 00:12:47.260
What were we to pray for?

00:12:47.260 --> 00:12:49.340
For wisdom and the Spirit of the Lord.

00:12:49.340 --> 00:13:00.999
Then that's when He was showing me this weapon that nobody knows about or perhaps they are ignoring because, at that point, for those that have watched the vision and watched me in the spirit, I said, "It's okay.

00:13:00.999 --> 00:13:01.279
It's okay.

00:13:01.559 --> 00:13:01.839
It's okay.

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:17.040
" The vision of wickedness and impending danger is due to some device hidden in a place unknown to the present intelligence—that's what I have to tell you—and maybe even ignored.

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:19.748
In other words, "Oh, that's not important.

00:13:19.748 --> 00:13:24.029
" This weapon is in a human mind.

00:13:24.029 --> 00:13:31.343
And the weapon that is in this human mind came to me when I saw some alphabetical letters.

00:13:31.343 --> 00:13:34.079
I saw some letters.

00:13:34.079 --> 00:13:36.816
At first, I thought it was A to Z.

00:13:36.816 --> 00:13:39.496
Now, this is a puzzle to me right now.

00:13:39.496 --> 00:13:47.760
But God almost said to me, "Focus on this so that the mystery can be unfolded.

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:51.839
" The letters were A and Q.

00:13:51.839 --> 00:13:52.1000
That's all I saw.

00:13:52.1000 --> 00:13:55.280
And He said, "That's where it's at.

00:13:55.280 --> 00:13:56.773
" Then I saw Russia.

00:13:56.773 --> 00:13:59.120
I saw Pakistan.

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:00.720
And I saw a connection.

00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:02.200
That's all I saw there.

00:14:02.200 --> 00:14:04.300
And I remember that, but I didn't say it.

00:14:04.300 --> 00:14:06.970
That's important for you to take note of.

00:14:06.970 --> 00:14:08.399
Go out there and research.

00:14:08.399 --> 00:14:10.739
Diana is going to as well.

00:14:10.739 --> 00:14:13.519
The vision of fire and water.

00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:19.320
Now I was absolutely surrounded by evil and I felt as Daniel did praying for his people.

00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:22.880
Now let me just tell you what Daniel said.

00:14:22.880 --> 00:14:34.240
He said, "While I was praying, the man Gabriel"—and remember Gabriel is one of the most powerful angels whom I'd seen in the vision at the beginning being caused to fly swiftly.

00:14:34.240 --> 00:14:37.560
Now you think about God and time.

00:14:37.560 --> 00:14:42.399
Why would God need an angel to move rapidly?

00:14:42.399 --> 00:14:48.613
Because, see, men have power to control things that happen on the earth because God put man on the earth.

00:14:48.613 --> 00:14:51.502
So when things happen, they can slow it down or they can hasten it.

00:14:53.369 --> 00:14:57.508
And so the angel was caused to fly swiftly.

00:14:57.508 --> 00:14:59.062
That's what Daniel says.

00:14:59.062 --> 00:15:02.382
And it reached me about the time of the evening offering.

00:15:02.382 --> 00:15:20.160
And I want you to get this because so few people realize and understand the power of the evening offering because he says the angel arrived and got to me about the time of the evening offering.

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:23.211
Russia was yielding from her...

00:15:23.211 --> 00:15:24.530
Now Russia would yield.

00:15:24.530 --> 00:15:28.663
Now I wasn't sure what that meant but I saw ashes, ashes, and ashes.

00:15:29.189 --> 00:15:39.909
And then suddenly out of the ashes arose a charmer, a man, a serpent in a man with seducing power as I'd not ever seen before.

00:15:39.909 --> 00:15:41.451
Keep your eye on Russia.

00:15:41.451 --> 00:15:43.467
Watch what happens.

00:15:43.467 --> 00:15:44.853
Wasn't that amazing?

00:15:44.853 --> 00:15:49.839
So Kim Clement saw something that was just pretty radical, wasn't it?

00:15:49.839 --> 00:15:52.760
You know, and his worship—doesn't his worship just bless you?

00:15:53.029 --> 00:15:55.839
When he plays the piano and everything, it blesses me.

00:15:55.839 --> 00:15:58.702
I can sit down and hear the mountain of the Lord and just sit there and just weep.

00:15:58.702 --> 00:15:59.591
I just love it.

00:15:59.591 --> 00:16:01.740
I told Diana, I said, "It's one of my favorite songs.

00:16:01.740 --> 00:16:02.275
" I loved it.

00:16:02.275 --> 00:16:04.186
I don't know if he wrote that song or not.

00:16:04.186 --> 00:16:06.239
I'm sure he did, but it really blessed me.

00:16:06.239 --> 00:16:06.959
It still does.

00:16:06.959 --> 00:16:09.060
I listen to it probably once or twice a week.

00:16:09.060 --> 00:16:19.897
You know, the Lord warned me and He said, "Brandon, when a general in battle dies in the battle and the war is not over, it doesn't mean that their job is complete.

00:16:19.897 --> 00:16:25.892
It means they're passing the baton on to somebody else now, that another general comes up to take it.

00:16:25.892 --> 00:16:27.759
" And He said, "Run with it.

00:16:27.759 --> 00:16:29.508
Run with this.

